# Materials and Methods

This section should contain a detailed description of all the methods used during the project.

- If your project is a lab-based study, you must also describe the materials used and their origin. However detailed protocols are not usually required.
- If you had practical assistance in the collection of the data (e.g. if you were provided with samples by the project supervisor or if you were part of a team carrying out field work), thenthis must be clearly stated along with the role you played in generating the data specified.
